Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.67,0:02:08.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.44,0:02:12.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么突然要做这种事
